title: The Book of Ghosts

description: LibriVox recording of The Book of Ghosts, by Sabine Baring-Gould. Reverend Sabine Baring-Gould (1834-1924) was an English hagioprapher, antiquarian, novelist and eclectric scholar. During his life, he published more than 100 books, among them this collection of ghost stories.
